  "text": "Sc -positive cells that are formed by de-novo prion propagation after infection with prion-containing samples [CITATION_1] . A more sensitive version of the assay, the Scrapie cell assay at endpoint format (SCEPA) exploits the observation that the sensitivity for prion detection can be significantly improved by varying the cell splitting ratio [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] .",
